==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sponson
<hw>Spon"son</hw> <pr>(-s⟦ucr⟧n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Shipbuilding)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>One of the triangular
platforms in front of, and abaft, the paddle boxes of a steamboat.</def>
<sd>(b)</sd> <def>One of the slanting supports under the guards of a
steamboat.</def> <sd>(c)</sd> <def>One of the armored projections fitted
with gun ports, used on modern war vessels.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sponsor</ent>⟦br⟧
